In [7]:

    one_hot = pd.get_dummies(df[col])
    one_hot = one_hot.add_prefix(col + "_")
    df = df.drop(col, axis=1)
    df = pd.concat([df, one_hot], axis=1)

In [49]:
def pf_classifier_categorical(model, df):
    df.loc[:, df.dtypes == 'object'] =\
        df.select_dtypes(['object'])\
        .apply(lambda x: x.astype('category'))
    return model.predict_proba(df)[:, 1]

explainer_rf = dx.Explainer(model_rf, X_test, y_test, predict_function=pf_classifier_categorical, label="RFC")

gini_rf = sorted([(col, imp) for col, imp in zip(X_test.columns, model_rf.feature_importances_)], key=lambda x: x[1])[-5:]
gini_rf_cols, gini_rf_vals = zip(*gini_rf)

plt.bar(gini_rf_cols, gini_rf_vals)
plt.title("Gini-based Variable Importance")
plt.show()
